wicked band..!!! :D
thanx alot for d upload :)

Great torrent, thank you. Been dying to hear some Diamond Dave era albums.

A couple of things I might suggest though is that you include the 'Best Of' albums, or at least the tracks off them that were recorded for those albums. Also, I noticed that on the album F.U.C.K. the last track (Top of the World) was missing. Would take this torrent from great to fan-f'n-tastic.
